snippet: Lewis recovered from a slow start with four birdies on the back nine to take a share of the lead with Caroline Hedwall of Sweden heading into the final round of the L.P.G.A. Reignwood Classic in Beijing.
abstract: Stacy Lewis takes a share of the lead with Caroline Hedwall of Sweden heading into the final round of the Reignwood LPGA Classic in Beijing; other golf news noted.
